E%26quot%3BOur%20allies%20and%20partners%20know%20very%20well%20how%20much%20this%20President%20respects%20them...He%20was%20making%20a%20broad%20comment%20speaking%20about%20this%20(US)%20country%2C%20speaking%20about%20how%20important%20it%20is%20to%20be%20a%20country%20of%20immigrants%20and%20how%20it%20makes%20our%20country%20stronger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Press%20Secretary%20stressed%20that%20Biden's%20focus%20remains%20on%20bolstering%20diplomatic%20relationships%20with%20nations%20such%20as%20India%20and%20Japan%2C%20evident%20in%20his%20actions%20over%20the%20past%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20we%20have%20a%20strong%20relationship%20with%2C%20India%20with%20Japan%2C%20and%20the%20President%20if%20you%20just%20look%20at%20the%20last%20three%20years%20has%20certainly%20focused%20on%20those%20diplomatic%20relationships%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20broader%20case%20that%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20make%2C%26quot%3B%20Jean%20Pierre%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20most%20leaders%20and%20allies%20across%20the%20globe%20understand%20that%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20who%20we%20are%20as%20a%20nation%2C%20we%20are%20a%20nation%20of%20immigrants.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20the%20significance%20of%20America's%20immigrant%20identity%2C%20she%20reiterated%20Biden's%20belief%20that%20diversity%20strengthens%20the%20nation.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20in%20our%20DNA.%20You%20have%20heard%20the%20President%20say%20it%2C%20it%20makes%20us%20better%2C%20and%20we%20are%20stronger%20for%20it%20and%20that%20is%20a%20very%20important%20point%20to%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20Jean%20Pierre%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%20were%20made%20at%20a%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20fundraiser%20that%20marked%20the%20start%20of%20Asian%20American%2C%20Native%20Hawaiian%20and%20Pacific%20Islander%20Heritage%20Month%2C%20which%20celebrates%20diversity%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20%26quot%3BOne%20of