fs-opentowork-activity-7191417329157595136-acTL%2F%3Ftrk%3Dpublic_profile%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%20about%20losing%20their%20Tesla%20internships%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well.%20Gura%20said%20several%20interns%20have%20connected%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20cuts%20and%20are%20offering%20support%20to%20one%20another.%20She%20feels%20lucky%20compared%20to%20other%20interns%20who%20had%20already%20paid%20for%20flights%20and%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGura%20said%20she's%20trying%20to%20stay%20positive%20and%20look%20to%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaking%20the%20time%20to%20think%20about%20this%2C%20I%20have%20learned%20that%20rejection%20is%20redirection%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20on%20LinkedIn.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20I%20am%20incredibly%20disappointed%20that%20I%20will%20not%20have%20the%20summer%20I%20intended%20to%20have%2C%20I%20know%20that%20this%20moment%20will%20only%20help%20me%20grow%20stronger%20as%20a%20professional.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20can't%20help%20but%20feel%20disappointed%20by%20the%20whole%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20bummed%20me%20out%20the%20most%20is%20I%20didn't%20even%20have%20the%20chance%20to%20showcase%20my%20skills%2C%26quot%3B%20Gura%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-internship-texas-layoffs-revoked-college-student-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714692284000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6634011e10dfcda4096641c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-internship-texas-layoffs-revoked-college-student-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Brook%20Gura%20was%20supposed%20to%20start%20interning%20at%20Tesla%20later%20this%20month.%20Now%2C%20she's%20scrambling%20after%20Tesla%20revoked%20her%20offer%20amid%20personnel%20cuts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22esnodgrass%40insider.com%