0knows%20little%20about%20Kennedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%2C%20uh%2C%20not%20a%20serious%20candidate%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20on%20Thursday.%20%26quot%3BThey%20say%20he%20hurts%20Biden.%20I%20don't%20know%20who%20he%20hurts%2C%20he%20might%20hurt%20me.%20I%20don't%20know.%20He%20has%20very%20low%20numbers%2C%20certainly%20not%20numbers%20that%20he%20can%20debate%20with.%20He's%20got%20to%20get%20his%20numbers%20a%20lot%20higher%20before%20he's%20credible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20polling%20has%20also%20shown%20that%20Kennedy's%20inclusion%20hurts%20Trump.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20NBC%20News%20national%20poll%20found%20that%20Trump%20led%20Biden%20by%20two%20points%2C%20but%20when%20Kennedy%20and%20other%20third-party%20hopefuls%20were%20added%2C%20Biden%20ended%20up%20with%20a%20two-point%20lead.%20It%20should%20be%20noted%20both%20outcomes%20are%20within%20the%20margin%20of%20error%20and%20illustrate%20the%20extremely%20close%20margin%20of%20the%20race%20entering%20the%20summer.%20According%20to%20FiveThirtyEight's%20weighted%20national%20polling%20average%2C%20Kennedy%20is%20polling%20at%2010%25%20while%20Trump%20and%20Biden%20are%20at%2041.4%25%20and%2040.8%25%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20president's%20barrage%20of%20criticism%20comes%20after%20Kennedy%20showed%20genuine%20efforts%20to%20appeal%20to%20Trump%20voters.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20noted%20vaccine%20skeptic%20has%20refused%20to%20rule%20out%20recalling%20the%20Moderna%20COVID-19%20shot%2C%20a%20position%20held%20by%20his%20running%20mate%2C%20Nicole%20Shanahan.%20Kennedy%20has%20also%20expressed%20sympathy%20for%20some%20Americans%20convicted%20of%20charges%20related%20to%20the%20January%206%2C%202021%2C%20Capitol%20riot.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Politico%20reported%2C%20Kennedy%20has%20repeatedly%20appeared%20on%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F05%2F01%2Frfk-jr-trump-2024-elections-00155425%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMAGA-aligned%20podcasts%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20shows.%20Kennedy%20rose%20to%20initial%20fame%20as%20an%20environmentalist%20in%20line%20with%20his%20family's%20well-known%20liberal%20views%2C%20but%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20he%20has%20found%20much%20more%20in%20common%20with%20the%20right-wing.%20He%20abandoned%20his%20primary%20challenge%20to%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20in%20favor%20of%20an%20independent%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20refusal%20to%20debate%20Kennedy%20may%20not%20be%20entirely%20in%20his%20hands.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nonprofit%20Commission%20on%20Presidential%20Debates%2C%20created%20by%20both%20major%20US%20parties%2C%20has%20hosted%20every%20presidential%20debate%20since%201988.%20The%20commission%20has%20faced%20intense%20criticism%20over%20its%20treatment%20of%20third-party%20candidates.%20It%20allowed%20Texas%20businessman%20Ross%20Perot%20to%20participate%20in%20all%20three%20debates%20in%201992%20but%20blocked%20him%20four%20years%20later.%20No%20third-party%20candidate%20has%20come%20close%20to%20surpassing%20Perot's%20mark%20of%20nearly%2019%25%20of%20the%20popular%20vote%20he%20received%20in%201992.%20Since%202000%2C%20the%20commission%20has%20imposed%20a%2015%25%20threshold%20in%20major%20national%20polls%2C%20which%20no%20third-party%20challenger%20has%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Trump%20and%20his%20allies%20have%20been%20harshly%20critical%20of%20the%20debate%20commission.%20The%20Republican%20National%20Committee%20voted%20in%202022%20to%20leave%20the%20commission.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20Trump's%20campaign%20managers%20threatened%20to%20hold%20a%20debate%20without%20the%20commission%20if%20they%20refused%20the%20former%20president's%20request%20to%20move%20up%20the%20first%20debate%2C%20which%20is%20set%20for%20September%2016%20at%20Texas%20State%20University%20in%20San%20Marcos%2C%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20recently%20told%20radio%20host%20Howard%20Stern%20that%20he%20would%20like%20to%20debate%20Trump%2C%20but%20there%