%20its%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20there%20were%20%26quot%3Bseveral%20issues%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20operation%20but%20did%20not%20explain%20exactly%20how%20it%20failed%20to%20identify%20its%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMasto%2C%20a%20shepherd%2C%20was%2056%20years%20old%20and%20living%20in%20the%20Syrian%20town%20of%20Qorqanya.%20On%20the%20day%20he%20died%2C%20an%20American%20Predator%20drone%20tracked%20him%20down%20and%20fired%20Hellfire%20missile%2C%20which%20landed%20behind%20his%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Central%20Command's%20investigation%2C%20the%20strike%20was%20conducted%20in%20compliance%20with%20Central%20Command%20and%20Department%20of%20Defense%20policies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20law%20of%20armed%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20defense%20official%20told%20The%20Washington%20Post%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20that%20the%20American%20drone%20strike%20was%20botched%20due%20to%20the%20decision-making%20and%20accuracy%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Bconfirmation%20bias%20and%20insufficient%20red%20teaming%26quot%3B%20issues%20among%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Washington%20Posted%20determined%20that%20it's%20still%20unclear%20who%20the%20intended%20target%20was%20and%20whether%20anyone%20will%20be%20held%20accountable%20for%20the%20inaccurate%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECentral%20Command%20said%20in%20its%20statement%20Thursday%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Backnowledges%20and%20regrets%20the%20civilian%20harm%20that%20resulted%20from%20the%20airstrike%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20CENTCOM%20takes%20%26quot%3Ball%20reports%20of%20civilian%20harm%20caused%20by%20U.S.%20military%20operations%20seriously%20and%20continue%20to%20employ%20thorough%20and%20deliberate%20targeting%20and%20strike%20processes%20to%20minimize%20civilian%20harm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20a%20first.%20The%20US%20military%20has%20made%20other%20similar%20mistakes%20in%20the%20past%2C%20such%20as%20when%20it%20initially%20celebrated%20eliminating%20an%20imminent%20threat%20with%20a%20fatal%20drone%20strike%20during%20the%20Afghanistan%20withdrawal%20only%20to%20discover%20later%20that%20it%20actually%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-drone-strike-targeted-aid-worker-killing-10-afghan-civilians-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekilled%20an%20aid%20worker%20and%20nine%20others%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20seven%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20New%20York%20Times%20investigation%20first%20brought%20that%20deadly%20incident%20to%20light.%20None%20of%20the%20service%20members%20involved%20in%20that%20strike%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fno-troops-involved-in-botched-drone-strike-will-be-punished-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewere%20punished%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Civilians%20have%2C%20on%20many%20occasions%2C%20been%20collateral%20damage%20in%20the%20wars%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-forces-mistakenly-kill-syrian-civilian-in-drone-strike-report-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714681453000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6633f61d0dfb1341e902142b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-forces-mistakenly-kill-syrian-civilian-in-drone-strike-report-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20forces%20accidentally%20killed%20Mr.%20Lufti%20Hasan%20Masto%20in%20a%20drone%20strike%2C%20mistaking%20him%20for%20a%20senior%20Al%20Qaeda%20leader%2C%20reveals%20a%20Washington%20Post%20probe.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Ella%20Sherman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-forces-mistakenly-kill-syrian-civilian-in-drone-strike-report-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bosco%3A%20Remo%20and%20I%20have%20not%20rec