g%20worse%20than%20bots%20talking%20to%20bots.%20It%20is%20bots%20talking%20to%20bots%2C%20bots%20talking%20to%20bots%20at%20the%20direction%20of%20humans%2C%20humans%20talking%20to%20humans%2C%20humans%20talking%20to%20bots%2C%20humans%20arguing%20about%20a%20fake%20thing%20made%20by%20a%20bot%2C%20humans%20talking%20to%20no%20one%20without%20knowing%20it%2C%20hijacked%20human%20accounts%20turned%20into%20bots%2C%20humans%20worried%20that%20the%20other%20humans%20they're%20talking%20to%20are%20bots%2C%20hybrid%20human%2Fbot%20accounts%2C%20the%20end%20of%20a%20shared%20reality%2C%20and%2C%20at%20the%20center%20of%20all%20of%20this%3A%20One%20of%20the%20most%20valuable%20companies%20on%20the%20planet%20enabling%20this%20shitshow%20because%20its%20human%20executives%20and%20shareholders%20have%20too%20much%20money%20riding%20on%20the%20mass%20adoption%20of%20a%20reality-breaking%20technology%20to%20do%20anything%20about%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Ch2%3ERead%20more%20from%20404%20Media%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.404media.co%2Ffacebooks-ai-spam-isnt-the-dead-internet-its-the-zombie-internet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook's%20AI%20Spam%20Isn't%20the%20'Dead%20Internet'%3A%20It's%20the%20Zombie%20Internet%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20take%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20weird%20and%20sometimes%20unsettling%20nature%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-imagine-ai-image-generator-morphs-as-you-type-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20images%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20fascinating%2C%20but%20underneath%20the%20phenomenon%20of%20these%20AI-powered%20pages%20proliferating%2C%20there%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20classic%20case%20of%20traditional%20engagement%20bait.%20The%20AI%20stuff%20builds%20up%20a%20page's%20following%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20that%20can%20be%20profitable%20for%20the%20page%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20I'm%20left%20with%20is%20why%20is%20Facebook%20allowing%20this%3F%20404%20Media's%20report%20notes%20that%20occasionally%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20take%20action%20against%20certain%20pages%2C%20but%20only%20in%20really%20specific%20cases%20%E2%80%94%20like%20with%20a%20hacked%20account%20and%20when%20it%20removed%20AI-generated%20images%20of%20disfigured%20children.%20Those%20probably%20ran%20afoul%20of%20some%20other%20existing%20content%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20few%20theories%20about%20why%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-apps%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20(for%20now)%20allowing%20this%20kind%20of%20AI%20image%20spam%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20election%20year%2C%20and%20Facebook%20has%20bigger%20content-moderation%20issues%20to%20deal%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20images%20themselves%20are%20mostly%20benign%2C%20and%20the%20individual%20images%20don't%20run%20afoul%20of%20content%20guidelines.%20Shrimp%20Jesus%20is%20absurd%2C%20and%20things%20like%20it%20may%20ruin%20the%20Facebook%20experience%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20but%20for%20now%2C%20it's%20not%20really%20an%20issue%20of%20violating%20the%20content%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EEngagement%20bait%20isn't%20necessarily%20a%20banned%20tactic%2C%20either.%20Nothing%20says%20you%20can't%20post%20lots%20of%20engaging%20content%20to%20trick%20boomers%20(and%20others)%20into%20commenting.%20There%20are%20ways%20to%20violate%20the%20rules%20with%20certain%20spam%20tactics%2C%20but%20maybe%20these%20AI-fueled%20accounts%20aren't%20crossing%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EFacebook%20will%20start%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fmeta-to-launch-ai-image-label-on-facebook-instagram-threads-1033036612%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edetect%20and%20label%20some%20AI-generated%20images%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20there's%20no%20rule%20that%20says%20you%20can't%20post%20something%20just%20because%20it's%20AI-generated.%20(When%20I%20asked%20about%20how%20they're%20handling%20these%2C%20a%20rep%20for%20Meta%20pointed%20me%20to%20their%20announcement%20of%20this%20policy.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E(404%20Media's%20theory)%3A%20Meta%20is%20so%20invested%20in%20AI%20that%20it%20wants%20us%20to%20get%20used%20to%20seeing%20AI%20images%2C%20and%20so%20they're%20willing%20to%20let%20it%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-ai-shrimp-jesus-zombie-internet-spam-content-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714680299000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6633e472ec0c69656900759b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-ai-shrimp-jesus-zombie-internet-spam-content-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bizzarro%20AI%20images%20have%20turned%20parts%20of%20Facebook%20into%20a%20sometimes%20strange%20place%2C%20404%20Media%20reports.%20Why%20isn't%20Meta%20doing%20anything%20about%20it%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A83%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-ai-shrimp-jesus-zombie-internet-spam-content-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi%20May%20Contest%20From%20Raebareli%2C%20Say%20Congress%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20may%20contest%20from%20family%20bastion%20Raebareli%20%E2%80%93%20the%20seat%20vacated%20recently%20by%20his%20mother%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20--%20and%20the%20party%20could%20field%20senior%20leader%20and%20longtime%20Gandhi%20family%20loyalist%20KL%20Sharma%20from%20Amethi%2C%20