e%2C%20first%2C%20my%20family%20was%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Raina%20said%20during%20an%20interaction%20on%20Lallantop.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714673640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-09%2F7dkafsu8_suresh-raina_625x300_06_September_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsuresh-rainas-cousin-killed-in-road-accident-in-dharamshala-5575493%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Saurabh%20Kumar%2CRaina's%20maternal%20cousin%2C%20and%20his%20friend%20Shubham%20from%20Kuthman%20died%20in%20a%20collision%20with%20a%20car%20near%20Gaggal%20airport%20on%20Wednesday%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20Skull-Cap%3A%20Badruddin%20Ajmal%20On%20Why%20His%20Party%20Is%20Not%20Part%20Of%20INDIA%20Bloc%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAIUDF%20chief%20and%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Assam's%20Dhubri%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20Maulana%20Badaruddin%20Ajmal%20claimed%20that%20he%20could%20not%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20because%20he%20was%20told%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20did%20not%20want%20a%20skull-cap-wearing%20bearded%20man%20in%20the%20alliance%20fearing%20an%20adverse%20impact%20on%20the%20Hindus%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20fear%2C%20I%20was%20told%20straight.%20I%20spoke%20to%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20who%20initially%20was%20the%20architect%20of%20this%20new%20bloc.%20He%20told%20me%20straight%3A%20'Rahul%20Gandhi%20does%20not%20want%20you%20to%20be%20part%20of%20this%20since%20it%20will%20affect%20Hindu%20votes.%20They%20don't%20want%20any%20bearded%20and%20skull-cap-wearing%20person%20to%20be%20part%20of%20it.'%20But%20I%20feel%20after%20this%20election%2C%20they%20will%20need%20me.%20There%20might%20be%20a%20new%20third%20front.%20That's%20what%20I%20feel%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Assam%2C%20where%20in%20Pha