0Ananda%20Bose%20has%20denied%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20an%20employee%20of%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%2C%20calling%20it%20an%20%26quot%3Bengineered%20narrative%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIf%20anybody%20wants%20some%20election%20benefits%20by%20maligning%20me%2C%20God%20bless%20them.%20But%20they%20cannot%20stop%20my%20fight%20against%20corruption%20and%20violence%20in%20Bengal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Raj%20Bhavan%2C%20in%20a%20series%20of%20posts%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BTo%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20staff%20who%20expressed%20solidarity%20with%20Hon'ble%20Governor%20Dr.%20C.%20V.%20Ananda%20Bose%20against%20whom%20some%20derogatory%20narratives%20were%20circulated%20by%20two%20disgruntled%20employees%20as%20agents%20of%20political%20parties%2C%20Hon'ble%20Governor%20said%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BTruth%20shall%20triumph.%20I%20refuse%20to%20be%20cowed%20down%20by%20engineered%20narratives.%20If%20anybody%20wants%20some%20election%20benefits%20by%20maligning%20me%2C%20God%20Bless%20them.%20But%20they%20cannot%20stop%20my%20fight%20against%20corruption%20and%20violence%20in%20Bengal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Raj%20Bhavan%20Kolkata%20(%40BengalGovernor)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBengalGovernor%2Fstatus%2F1786066050192155008%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%202%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20surfaced%20ahead%20of%20a%20visit%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20PM%20Modi%20is%20in%20Kolkata%20and%20is%20spending%20the%20night%20at%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20sources%20said%20this%20afternoon%2C%20a%20woman%20claiming%20to%20be%20a%20temporary%20staff%20member%20attached%20to%20the%20Peace%20Room%20in%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20had%20approached%20the%20police%20post%20located%20inside%20the%20Governor's%20House%20and%20accused%20Mr%20Bose%20of%20molesting%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20local%20police%20station%20at%20Hare%20Street%2C%20where%20she%20filed%20a%20complaint%2C%20in%20which%20she%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20molested%20multiple%20times%20by%20the%20Governor%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20have%20come%20as%20a%20boon%20to%20the%20state's%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20which%20had%20been%20smarting%20over%20the%20sex%20harassment%20allegations%20against%20its%20now%20suspended%20leader%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20at%20Sandeshkhali.%20The%20Governor%20was%20among%20the%20first%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20women%20from%20Sandeshkhali%20and%20made%20harsh%20remarks%20about%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Trinamool%20leader%20Shashi%20Panja%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20utterly%20shocked.%20The%20same%20Governor%20who%20reached%20Sandeshkhali%20talking%20about%20women's%20rights%20has%20now%20been%20involved%20in%20a%20rather%20shameful%20incident.%20He%20has%20sabotaged%20the%20reputation%20of%20his%20post%20and%20his%20chair%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20can%20be%20more%20shameful%20than%20a%20Governor%20getting%20involved%20in%20such%20heinous%20crimes%20and%20that%20too%20in%20the%20Raj%20Bhawan...%20Today%20the%20PM%20is%20coming%20to%20the%20state%20and%20he%20will%20stay%20at%20the%20Raj%20Bhawan.%20We%20want%20to%20know%20his%20reaction%20to%20the%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJournalist-turned-politician%20Sagarika%20Ghosh%20called%20the%20matter%20%26quot%3Bshocking%20and%20horrifying%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EBIG.%20Bengal%20governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%20accused%20of%20molesting%20a%20woman.%20How%20utterly%20APPALLING%20and%20HORRIFYING.%20Ahead%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40narendramodi%3C%2Fa%3E%20visit%20to%20Kolkata%20who%20is%20supposed%20to%20stay%20overnight%20at%20Raj%20Bhavan%2C%20a%20woman%20has%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20molested%20while%20she%20went%20to%20meet%20the%20Governor%20at%20Raj%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Sagarika%20Ghose%20(%40sagarikaghose)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsagarikaghose%2Fstatus%2F1786039811452629400%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%202%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20comes%20amid%20a%20massive%20row%20about%20sexual%20assault%20allegations%20against%20a%20Karnataka%20MP%2C%20over%20which%20the%20BJP%20is%20facing%20criticism%20from%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrajwal%20Revanna%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20BJP%20ally%20Janata%20Dal%20Secular%20and%20the%20grandson%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda%2C%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20raping%20multiple%20women.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20have%20distanced%20themselves%20from%20the%20matter%20and%20the%20Hasan%20MP%2C%20said%20to%20be%20in%20Germany%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20has%20been%20suspended%20by%20his%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714672320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F0jrilofo_bengal-governor-cv-ananda-bose-pti_625x300_14_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-governor-denies-sexual-harassment-allegation-by-raj-bhavan-employee-calls-it-engineered-narrative-5574973%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengal%20Governor%20denies%20sexual%20harassment%20allegation%20by%20Raj%20Bhavan%20employee%2C%20calls%20it%20%26quot%3Bengineered%20narrative%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbe