%20is%20a%20feeling%20that%20Narendra%20Modi%20would%20never%20understand%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20shredding%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20comments%20on%20dynastic%20politics%20and%20inheritance%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20had%20said%20last%20week%20that%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20had%20abolished%20inheritance%20tax%20after%20coming%20to%20power%20so%20that%20the%20wealth%20he%20had%20inherited%20from%20his%20mother%20would%20not%20be%20taxed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20speaking%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Morena%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Modi-ji%20stands%20on%20the%20dais%20and%20calls%20my%20father%20a%20traitor%2C%20when%20he%20says%20he%20changed%20a%20law%20to%20take%20his%20inheritance%20from%20his%20mother...%20he%20would%20not%20understand%20that%20my%20father%20did%20not%20get%20any%20wealth%20by%20way%20inheritance%2C%20he%20only%20got%20the%20thoughts%20of%20martyrdom%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20age%20of%2019%2C%20when%20I%20brought%20home%20the%20mangled%20remains%20of%20my%20father%2C%20I%20was%20upset%20with%20this%20country.%20I%20thought%2C%20'I%20had%20sent%20my%20father.%20It%20was%20your%20job%20to%20ensure%20his%20safety.%20I%20placed%20him%20in%20your%20care%2C%20but%20you%20returned%20me%20his%20remains%20wrapped%20in%20the%20national%20flag'.%20I%20had%20misgivings.%20I%20know%20what%20is%20the%20meaning%20of%20martyrdom.%20Today%20I%20am%2052%20and%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20I'm%20talking%20about%20it%20in%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20when%2040%20soldiers%20died%20in%20Pulwama%20in%202019%2C%20she%20had%20visited%20some%20of%20their%20families%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20There%2C%20the%20children%20of%20the%20martyrs%20told%20her%20that%20they%20want%20to%20join%20the%20army.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20one%20girl%20whose%20brother%20was%20in%20the%20Air%20force.%20She%20said%20'Didi%20I%20want%20to%20join%20the%20air%20force%20and%20become%20a%20pilot'%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20feeling%20of%20martyrdom.%20Modi-ji%20will%20never%20understand%20this.%20Modi-ji%20says%20whatever%20he%20likes%20about%20a%20martyr%20like%20Indira-ji.%20He%20only%20sees%20dynastic%20politics%2C%20he%20never%20sees%20patriotism%2C%20service%20to%20the%20nation.%20He%20would%20never%20understand%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20rally%20in%20Morena%20last%20week%2C%20PM%20Modi%20had%20said%20that%20earlier%2C%20half%20of%20a%20deceased%20person's%20wealth%20went%20to%20the%20government%20by%20law.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20talk%20then%20that%20Indira-ji%20had%20willed%20her%20wealth%20in%20her%20son%20Rajiv%20Gandhi's%20name.%20To%20save%20the%20money%20going%20to%20the%20government%20(after%20her%20death)%2C%20then%20PM%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20abolished%20the%20inheritance%20tax%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20ripping%20into%20the%20Congress%20over%20wealth%20redistribution%20and%20inheritance%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20benefitting%20from%20the%20abolition%20of%20estate%20duty%2C%20the%20Congress%20now%20wants%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20levy%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714669920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fsi9b4h4k_priyanka-gandhi-vadra-morena-_625x300_02_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-priyanka-gandhi-congress-my-father-inherited-martyrdom-not-wealth-priyanka-gandhi-responds-to-pm-5574422%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress's%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20today%20said%20her%20father%2C%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20had%20not%20inherited%20wealth%20but%20martyrdom%20from%20his%20mother.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-priyanka-gandhi-congress-my-father-inher