20of%20talks%20will%20be%20held%20very%20soon%20to%20%26quot%3Btake%20things%20forward%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20ongoing%20talks%20between%20India%20and%20China%20at%20diplomatic%20and%20military%20levels.%20These%20issues%20are%20serious%20and%20therefore%20they%20take%20time.%20We%20will%20have%20the%20next%20round%20of%20engagement%20very%20soon%20to%20take%20things%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20round%20of%20military%20talks%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20had%20taken%20place%20in%20February.%20In%20the%20talks%2C%20both%20sides%20agreed%20to%20maintain%20%26quot%3Bpeace%20and%20tranquillity%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20ground%20but%20there%20was%20no%20indication%20of%20any%20breakthrough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20troops%20are%20locked%20in%20a%20standoff%20in%20certain%20friction%20points%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%20even%20as%20the%20two%20sides%20completed%20disengagement%20from%20several%20areas%20following%20extensive%20diplomatic%20and%20military%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714668840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F9d672loo_randhir-jaiswal_625x300_02_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-says-shaksgam-valley-ours-on-china-construction-activity-reports-5574952%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Shaksgam%20Valley%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20territory%20of%20India%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20said%20today%20amid%20reports%20of%20China%20building%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20valley.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-says-shaksgam-valley-ours-on-china-construction-activity-reports-5574952%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-says-shaksgam-valley-ours-on-china-construction-activity-reports-5574952%2F