20fall%20to.%20They%20have%20now%20rewarded%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20accused%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20many%20of%20our%20women%20wrestlers%2C%20with%20a%20ticket%20for%20his%20son.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20party%20with%20no%20moral%20compass%2C%20led%20by%20a%20man%20whose%20only%20anchor%20is%20his%20desire%20for%20boundless%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ramesh%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20in%20Hindi%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20MP%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFather%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh's%20ticket%20to%20son.%20Do%20you%20talk%20of%20giving%20justice%20to%20women%20like%20this%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20put%20one's%20hat%20on%20another's%20head.%20You%20are%20trying%20to%20fool%20the%20people.%20Shameful%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20also%20slammed%20the%20BJP%20for%20giving%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20ticket%20to%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh's%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETMC%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sagarika%20Ghose%20said%20the%20BJP%20dropping%20incumbent%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20only%20to%20field%20his%20son%20from%20the%20Kaiserganj%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20UP%20is%20%26quot%3Bshameful%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20case%20of%20%26quot%3Bpolitics%20of%20proxy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20shows%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20condemn%20the%20%26quot%3Bsexual%20assault%26quot%3B%20committed%20by%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20the%20BJP%20has%20given%20a%20ticket%20to%20Karan%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20the%20son%20of%20its%20former%20star%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20is%20shameful%20and%20disgraceful.%20Mr%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20serious%20sexual%20assault%20by%20none%20other%20than%20India's%20Olympic%20medal-winning%20women%20wrestlers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrij%20Bhushan%20Singh%2C%20who%20stepped%20down%20from%20the%20post%20amid%20a%20raging%20protest%20against%20him%20over%20the%20sexual%20harassment%20allegations%20by%20women%20wrestlers%2C%20has%20denied%20the%20charges.%20The%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20also%20been%20accused%20under%20the%20POCSO%20(Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences)%20Act%20for%20sexual%20offences%20against%20children...%20To%20give%20a%20ticket%20to%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh's%20son%20is%20nothing%20but%20the%20politics%20of%20proxy.%20Karan%20Singh%20is%20a%20proxy%20for%20his%20father%2C%26quot%3B%20Ghose%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20shows%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20not%20willing%20to%20condemn%20the%20sexual%20assault%20committed%20by%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%26quot%3B%20and%20its%20slogans%20on%20women%20empowerment%20are%20%26quot%3Bhollow%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20slogans%20of%20%26quot%3BNari%20Shakti%2C%20Nari%20Samman%20and%20Beti%20Bachao%26quot%3B%20are%20all%20%26quot%3Bhollow%2C%20shallow%2C%20meaningless%20and%20bogus%26quot%3B%2C%20Ms%20Ghose%20said%20and%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20says%20it%20stands%20for%20Nari%20Samman%20but%20has%20given%20a%20ticket%20to%20a%20proxy%20of%20someone%20who%20is%20accused%20of%20serious%20sexual%20assault%20and%20assault%20against%20women%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecond%2C%20BJP%20says%20it's%20against%20Parivarwad%20or%20family%20politics...%20What%20is%20this%20but%20dynastic%20politics%3F%20The%20fact%20is%2C%20Mr%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh's%20other%20son%20is%20already%20an%20MLA.%20Now%2C%20his%20other%20son%20has%20also%20got%20an%20MP%20ticket%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714664280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvi