e%2F2023-04%2F06%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1680776485-8017.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fdabur-india-q4fy24-results-net-profit-rises-16-2-to-rs-349-5-crore-124050201235_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20maker%20of%20Real%20fruit%20juices%20and%20Hajmola%20candy%20saw%20its%20rural%20business%20outpacing%20urban%20in%20the%20last%20quarter%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20growing%20distribution%20system%20in%20the%20rural%20areas%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fdabur-india-q4fy24-results-net-profit-rises-16-2-to-rs-349-5-crore-124050201235_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fdabur-india-q4fy24-results-net-profit-rises-16-2-to-rs-349-5-crore-124050201235_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fdabur-india-q4fy24-results-net-profit-rises-16-2-to-rs-349-5-crore-124050201235_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Viagra%20Maker's%20Plea%2C%20Court%20Bars%20Use%20of%20'Vigoura'%20Name%20By%20Homeopathy%20Firm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20permanently%20restrained%20the%20use%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BVigoura%26quot%3B%20mark%20by%20a%20homeopathic%20drug%20manufacturer%20for%20selling%20its%20medicine%20for%20sexual%20disorders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court's%20decision%20came%20on%20a%20lawsuit%20for%20trademark%20infringement%20filed%20by%20Pfizer%20Products%20Inc.%2C%20which%20sells%20a%20well-recognised%20erectile%20dysfunction%20allopathic%20drug%20under%20the%20%26quot%3BViagra%26quot%3B%20trademark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20there%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20potential%26quot%3B%20for%20confusion%20between%20the%20two%20names%20because%20of%20their%20resemblances%20and%20overlap%20in%20commercial%20operations%2C%20Justice%20Sanjeev%20Narula%20directed%20Renovision%20Exports%20Private%20Limited%20not%20to%20use%20%26quot%3BVigoura%26quot%3B%20or%20any%20other%20mark%20that%20is%20%26quot%3Bdeceptively%20similar%26quot%3B%20to%20Pfizer's%20trademark%20%26quot%3BViagra%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20ruled%20that%20the%20petitioner%20shall%20be%20entitled%20to%20nominal%20damages%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%2C%20recoverable%20jointly%20and%20severally%20from%20the%20defendant%20entity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20defendants%20or%20anyone%20acting%20on%20their%20behalf%20are%20permanently%20restrained%20from%20manufacturing%2C%20selling%20or%20offering%20for%20sale%2C%20marketing%2C%20advertising%20or%20in%20any%20other%20manner%20using%20the%20mark%20'VIGOURA'%20or%20any%20mark%20deceptively%20similar%20to%20the%20plaintiff's%20trademark%20'VIAGRA'%20in%20relation%20to%20any%20of%20their%20goods%20as%20would%20amount%20to%20infringement%20or%20passing%20off%20of%20the%20plaintiff's%20registered%20mark%20'VIAGRA'%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%20in%20its%20order%20passed%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlaintiff's%20trademark%20'VIAGRA'%20is%20highly%20recognised%20by%20its%20name%20in%20the%20sphere%20of%20erectile%20dysfunction%20drugs.%20They%20have%20invested%20heavily%20in%20building%20a%20brand%20and%20owing%20to%20its%20success%2C%20'VIAGRA'%20has%20acquired%20national%20and%20global%20repute.%20Consequently%2C%20the%20defendants'%20subsequent%20adoption%20of%20the%20impugned%20mark%20with%20the%20knowledge%20of%20the%20plaintiff's%20existence%20warrants%20an%20award%20of%20damages%20in%20the%20plaintiff's%20favour%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20observed%20that%20there%20was%20material%20that%20successfully%20proved%20Pfizer's%20status%20as%20the%20proprietor%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BViagra%26quot%3B%20trademark%20and%20the%20company's%20successful%20registration%20in%20India%20further%20proved%20its%20exclusive%20ownership%20over%20the%20mark%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20%26quot%3BVigoura%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BViagra%26quot%3B%20exhibited%20a%20high%20degree%20of%20phonetic%20similarity%20that%20could%20mislead%20consumers%20into%20believing%20that%20the%20former%20was%20either%20a%20variant%20of%20or%20endorsed%20by%20the%20makers%20of%20%26quot%3BViagra%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20overall%20length%20of%20the%20words%20and%20their%20similar%20letter%20arrangements%20can%20cause%20confusion%20at%20a%20glance%2C%20especially%20in%20environments%20where%20consumers%20make%20quick%20decisions%2C%20such%20as%20online%20searches%20or%20pharmacy%20purchases%2C%20the%20judge%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20initial%20confusion%20can%20occur%20regardless%20of%20the%20consumer's%20overall%20awareness%20or%20knowledge%20of%20the%20differences%20between%20allopathic%20and%20homeopathic%20remedies.%20In%20such%20scenarios%2C%20while%20the%20consumer%20might%20understand%20the%20distinctions%20between%20the%20kinds%20of%20treatment%20(allopathic%20versus%20homeopathic)%2C%20the%20resemblance%20in%20the%20ailment%20intended%20to%20be%20cured%20and%20the%20names%20or%20trademarks%20can%20induce%20an%20association%20between%20the%20two%20products%2C%20based%20on%20perceived%20endorsements%20or%20verbal%20accounts%20or%20recommendations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20view%20of%20the%20resemblances%20between%20the%20two%20trademarks%20and%20the%20overlap%20in%20the%20field%20of%20use%20and%20commercial%20operations%2C%20as%20elucidated%20above%2C%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20potential%20for%20confusion%20amongst%20the%20general%20public.%20Thus%2C%20the%20court%20answers%20this%20issue%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20plaintiff%20and%20against%20the%20defendants%2C%20holding%20that%20the%20defendants'%20'VIGOURA'%20mark%20infringes%20the%20plaintiff's%20registered%20'VIAGRA'%20mark%20under%20sections%2029(1)%20and%2029(2)(b)%20of%20the%20Trademarks%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714661940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-12%2Fgeneric-versions-of-viagra-will-be-available-soon_650x400_61513158218.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-viagra-makers-plea-court-bars-use-of-vigoura-name-by-homeopathy-firm-5574203%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20permanently%20restrained%20the%20use%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BVigoura%26quot%3B%20mark%20by%20a%20homeopathic%20drug%20manufacturer%20for%20selling%20its%20medicine%20for%20sexual%20disorders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-viagra-makers-plea-court-bars-use-of-vigoura-name-by-homeopathy-firm-5574203%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-viagra-makers-plea-court-bars-use-of-vigoura-name-by-homeopathy-firm-5574203%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-viagra-makers-plea-court-bars-use-of-vigoura-name-by-homeopathy-firm-5574203%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20tests%20advanced%20missile%20similar%20to%20one%20likely%20used%20by%20Israel%20on%20Iran%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714661719000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-05%2F02%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1714660467-7522.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Fchina-tests-advanced-missile-similar-to-one-likely-used-by-israel-on-iran-124050