%20carried%20out%20a%20Caesarian%20delivery%20using%20a%20cellphone%20torch.%20And%2C%20if%20the%20incident%20wasn't%20shocking%20enough%2C%20this%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20country's%20financial%20capital%20in%20a%20hospital%20run%20by%20India's%20richest%20civic%20body%20-%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%2C%20whose%20budget%20is%20over%20Rs%2052%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amount%20allocated%20for%20health%20is%2012%20per%20cent%2C%20or%20Rs%206%2C250%20crore.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhusruddin%20Ansari%2C%20who%20is%20specially%20abled%20and%20does%20not%20have%20a%20leg%2C%20got%20his%2026-year-old%20wife%20Sahidun%20admitted%20to%20the%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20maternity%20home%20for%20her%20delivery.%20The%20couple%20had%20been%20married%20only%20for%2011%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20has%20alleged%20that%20power%20went%20out%20in%20the%20maternity%20home%20on%20Monday%20and%20the%20generator%20wasn't%20turned%20on%20for%20three%20hours.%20They%20said%20that%20even%20after%20they%20lost%20the%20mother%20and%20child%2C%20another%20delivery%20was%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20darkness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20family%20have%20been%20protesting%20outside%20the%20hospital%20for%20days%20and%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(BMC)%20has%20finally%20ordered%20an%20inquiry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Incision%20Before%20Consent'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ansari's%20mother%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20daughter-in-law%20was%20absolutely%20healthy%20and%20had%20been%20pregnant%20for%20nine%20months.%20All%20her%20reports%20were%20okay.%20They%20took%20her%20for%20the%20delivery%20at%207%20am%20on%20April%2029%2C%20kept%20her%20the%20whole%20day%20and%2C%20until%208%20pm%2C%20we%20were%20told%20everything%20was%20fine.%20Doctors%20told%20us%20that%20the%20delivery%20would%20be%20normal.%20Then%2C%20when%20I%20went%20to%20meet%20her%2C%20I%20saw%20that%20she%20was%20covered%20in%20blood.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20had%20made%20an%20incision%20and%20then%20came%20to%20get%20a%20signature%20saying%20she%20had%20suffered%20a%20fit%20and%20a%20C-section%20was%20needed.%20That's%20when%20the%20power%20went%20out%20and%20they%20did%20not%20send%20us%20to%20another%20hospital%20even%20after%20that.%20They%20took%20us%20to%20the%20operation%20theatre%20and%20did%20the%20delivery%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20phone%20torch.%20The%20child%20died%20and%2C%20when%20we%20cried%2C%20the%20doctor%20said%20the%20mother%20would%20survive.%20They%20referred%20us%20to%20Sion%20Hospital%2C%20but%20she%20had%20died%20by%20then.%20There%20was%20no%20oxygen%20available%20either%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20alleged.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20inconsolable%20Mr%20Ansari%20has%20called%20for%20the%20doctors%20to%20be%20punished.%20%26quot%3BJust%20as%20I%20am%20suffering%2C%20the%20doctors%20and%20staff%20should%20suffer%2C%20they%20should%20be%20punished.%20The%20hospital%20should%20be%20closed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20justice.%20I%20earn%20a%20small%20amount%20and%20I%20am%20specially%20abled.%20I%20got%20married%20with%20great%20difficulty%2C%20my%20life%20has%20been%20ruined%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20rued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20also%20showed%20photos%20and%20videos%20of%20another%20delivery%20being%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20same%20operation%20theatre%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20cellphone%20torch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Need%20Strict%20Action'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20BMC%20councillor%20Jagruti%20Patil%20of%20the%20BJP%20said%20she%20has%20met%20the%20party%20candidate%2C%20Mihir%20Kotecha%2C%20from%20the%20Mumbai%20North%20East%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20-%20under%20which%20the%20hospital%20falls%20-%20and%20the%20BMC%20has%20finally%20taken%20action%20by%20setting%20up%20an%20inquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20condition%20of%20the%20hospital%20is%20bad.%20Such%20complaints%20have%20been%20made%20about%20this%20hospital%20earlier%20as%20well.%20Strict%20action%20will%20have%20to%20be%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714661100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Frl1rio7_delivery-by-torchlight_625x300_02_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-hospital-carries-out-delivery-using-phone-torch-mother-and-baby-die-5574010%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20pregnant%20mother%20and%20her%20baby%20have%20died%20after%20doctors%20at%20a%20hospital%20carried%20out%20a%20Caesarian%20delivery%20using%20a%20cellphone%20torch.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-hospital-carries-out-delivery-using-phone-torch-mother-and-baby-die-5574010%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-hospital-carries-out-delivery-using-phone-torch-mother-and-baby-die-5574010%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-hospital-carries-out-delivery-using-phone-torch-mother-and-baby-die-5574010%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Coal%20India%20registers%2017%25%20growth%20in%20annual%20profit%2C%20tepid%20income%20rise%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714660541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F02%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1690996539-0715.JPG%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fcoal-india-registers-17-growth-in-annual-profit-tepid-income-rise-124050201205_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Board%20recommends%20final%20dividend%20of%20Rs%205%20a%20share%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fr