es-food-safety-ethylene-oxide-fish-curry-masala-singapore-hong-kong%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFood%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Authority%20of%20India%20(FSSAI)%3C%2Fa%3E%20tests%20found%20that%2047%20out%20of%C2%A0168%20%3Cem%3Epaneer%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Ekhoya%20%3C%2Fem%3Eproducts%20were%20contaminated.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20a%20whopping%201%2C300%20kg%20of%20fake%20%3Cem%3Epaneer%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20discovered%20and%20disposed%20of%20by%20authorities%20along%20the%20Mumbai-Delhi%20Expressway.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20just%20the%20tip%20of%20the%20iceberg%20of%20many%20such%20%E2%80%98contaminated%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98synthetic%E2%80%99%20%3Cem%3Epaneer%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20this%2C%20how%20do%20you%20understand%20whether%20the%20%3Cem%3Epaneer%20%3C%2Fem%3Eyou%E2%80%99ve%20purchased%20is%20fake%20or%20real%3F%20Here%20are%20three%20simple%20steps%20to%20alleviate%20your%20worries%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Iodine%20Test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20a%20pan%20and%20boil%20%3Cem%3Epaneer%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20it.%20Add%20a%20few%20drops%20of%20iodine%20tincture%20to%20the%20boiled%20%3Cem%3Epaneer%3C%2Fem%3E.%20If%20it%20turns%20blue%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20artificial.%20If%20it%20retains%20its%20colour%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20pure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20The%20Dal%20Test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20the%20boiled%20paneer%20cool%20in%20water.%20Add%20some%20%3Cem%3Etoor%20dal%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20the%20water%20and%20let%20it%20rest%20for%2010%20minutes.%20If%20the%20water%20turns%20light%20red%2C%20the%20paneer%20may%20be%20contaminated.%20If%20the%20colour%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20change%2C%20go%20ahead%20and%20enjoy%20your%20paneer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20The%20Texture%20%26amp%3B%20Taste%20Test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20%3Cem%3Epaneer%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20you%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5