of%20them%20in%20Bangladesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20adds%20to%20the%20significance%20of%20Yunus%E2%80%99%20work%20is%20that%20the%20people%20he%20helped%20are%20those%20that%20traditional%20banks%20turned%20their%20backs%20on.%20A%20high%20risk%20of%20default%2C%20coupled%20with%20lending%20tiny%20loans%20at%20reasonable%20interest%2C%20formed%20the%20basis%20for%20the%20banks%E2%80%99%20reluctance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20way%20Yunus%20saw%20it%2C%20all%20these%20people%20needed%20was%20a%20chance.%20And%20so%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336695%2Finnovations-by-farmers-indian-agriculture-solar-dryer-biofertiliser-tree-scooter-organic-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fa%3E%20went%20on%20to%20start%20a%20full-fledged%20bank%20for%20Bangladesh%E2%80%99s%20poor%2C%20The%20Grameen%20Bank%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20poor%20as%20creditworthy.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20design%20of%20this%20internationally-acclaimed%20model%20made%20it%20to%20Yunus%E2%80%99%20book%20%E2%80%98Creating%20a%20World%20Without%20Poverty%E2%80%99.%20And%20when%20Ram%20laid%20hands%20on%20it%20in%202006%2C%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20put%20it%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Little%20Data%20Book%20on%20Financial%20Inclusion%202022%20(a%20pocket%20edition%20of%20the%20Global%20Findex%20Database)%2C%20India%20is%20behind%20Bangladesh%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20access%20to%20credit%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ram%20points%20out.%20%E2%80%9CAdd%20to%20this%20the%20high%20rate%20of%20interest%20and%20we%20began%20to%20ask%20ourselves%20why%20not%20do%20something%20similar%20in%20our%20country.%E2%80%9D%20The%20couple%20saw%20a%20P2P%20model%20as%20having%20a%20dual%20vantage%20%E2%80%94%20it%20would%20be%20profitable%20and%20sustainable%20for%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22