-builds-solar-power-eco-friendly-air-conditioner-exalta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20air%20conditioners%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20electricity%20as%20people%20try%20to%20escape%20the%20heat.%20%E2%80%9CWorking%20from%20home%20becomes%20more%20challenging%20as%20the%20temperature%20starts%20to%20rise%20as%20early%20as%207%20am.%20Living%20in%20apartments%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20us%20much%20room%20to%20naturally%20cool%20the%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vinaya%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20situation%20may%20seem%20bleak%2C%20architects%20and%20designers%20suggest%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20geography%2C%20a%20few%20steps%20to%20keep%20your%20home%20naturally%20cool.%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20spoke%20with%20several%20experts%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20secrets%20of%20designing%20a%20%E2%80%98cool%E2%80%99%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGoing%20Back%20To%20Your%20Roots%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20look%20back%20at%20the%20houses%20that%20our%20ancestors%20built%2C%20the%20structures%20with%20open%20spaces%2C%20inward-looking%20homes%20with%20courtyards%20and%20huge%20windows%20helped%20to%20keep%20the%20home%20naturally%20cool.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamira%20Rathod%2C%20an%20architect%20and%20designer%2C%20applied%20similar%20techniques%20to%20make%20a%20%E2%80%9CCool%20House%E2%80%9D%20located%20in%20Gujarat.%20The%20architect%20decided%20to%20utilise%20the%20wind%2C%20design%20and%20cooling%20materials%20to%20build%20and%20cool%20down%20the%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20architect%20suggests%20using%20the%20wind%20in%20a%20way%20that%20it%20travels%20through%20the%20home%20making%20it%20cooler.%20For%20the%20cool%20house%20located%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20she%20used%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctrack-like%20design%20with%20rooms%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20house%20with%20a%20courtyard%20to%20help%20the%20wind%20circulate.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C