com%2F348313%2Falwar-zero-cement-sustainable-home-rainwater-harvesting-neem-jaggery-built-by-shipra-singhania%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Once%20Featured%20in%20%E2%80%98Life%20of%20Pi%E2%80%99%2C%20This%20Puducherry%20Homestay%20is%20a%20200-YO%20Heritage%20Villa%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20morning%20last%20year%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20of%20Puducherry%20was%20fast%20asleep%2C%20Sudeep%20Sen%2C%20a%20Bengali%20poet%2C%20was%20working%20on%20a%20new%20piece.%20The%20protagonist%20was%20an%20iron%20safe%20embedded%20in%20a%20wall%20of%20his%20room%20at%20the%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20homestay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Room%204%2C%20the%20safe%20in%20the%20wall%20has%20not%20been%20opened%20in%20a%20150%20years%E2%80%A6It%20has%20seen%20history%2C%20life%20changing%2C%20aging%20%E2%80%94%20but%20no%20one%20knows%20what%20lies%20within.%20But%20what%20is%20inside%3F%20%E2%80%94%20The%20first%20owner%E2%80%99s%20ashes%2C%20her%20will%2C%20wealth%2C%20gold%3B%20old%20currencies%2C%20lover%E2%80%99s%20relics%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20stanzas%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20does%20make%20for%20a%20very%20compelling%20read%2C%20Siddarth%20Saikia%2C%20the%20owner%20and%20manager%20of%20affairs%20at%20the%20homestay%2C%20says%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20piece%20of%20fiction%3B%20the%20safe%20exists.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20key%20is%20lost%20in%20time%2C%20and%20the%20safe%E2%80%99s%20outer%20frame%20bears%20many%20markings.%20Many%20have%20tried%20to%20prise%20it%20open%20to%20check%20what%20it%20contains%2C%20but%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20budge%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20a%20professional%20locksmith%2C%20who%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20get%20through%2C%20informed%20Siddarth%20and%20the%20family%20that%20the%20safe%E2%80%99s%20rusted%20interiors%20and%20strategic%20position%20within%20the%20wall%20meant%20that%20the%20only%20way%20to%20crack%20it%20op