that%20the%20time%20had%20come%20for%20me%20to%20do%20something.%20Earlier%2C%20she%20was%20with%20me%2024%C3%977.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20brainstormed%20ideas%20about%20what%20we%20could%20start%2C%20but%20one%20thing%20was%20clear%20%E2%80%93%20it%20had%20to%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340611%2Fhealthy-snack-brand-startup-open-secret-woman-entrepreneur-ahana-gautam-iit-bombay-harvard%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efood-related%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prathima%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20over%2025%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20Fast-Moving%20Consumer%20Goods%20(FMCG)%20sector%2C%20Viswanath%20had%20a%20keen%20understanding%20of%20the%20market.%20Combined%20with%20Prathima%E2%80%99s%20passion%20for%20food%2C%20they%20found%20the%20winning%20combination%20in%20the%20ready-to-cook%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20food%20business%20as%20this%20is%20a%20universal%20need.%20In%20today%E2%80%99s%20busy%20world%2C%20food%20is%20available%20at%20the%20click%20of%20a%20button%2C%20but%20that%20is%20neither%20healthy%20nor%20sustainable.%20No%20one%20has%20the%20time%20to%20cook%2C%20but%20everyone%20wants%20simple%2C%20homemade%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrathima%20started%20researching%20and%20experimenting%20with%20products%20like%20curry%20paste%20and%20chutneys.%20She%20found%20that%20increasing%20their%20shelf%20life%20without%20adding%20preservatives%20would%20be%20difficult.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20thing%20that%20stood%20out%20during%20her%20market%20research%20was%20the%20demand%20for%20quick%20%3Cem%3Echapatis%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20adept%20at%20churning%20out%20%3Cem%3Echapatis%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20her%20family%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20equip%20herself%20with%20a%20pr